{"tid":137612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(現實問題) 奶媽定品客","createTime":"2017-02-28T03:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T06:20:36.000Z","uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9e801fd82048d508310d8d67fb4dd9bed35dd6","tid":137612,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"理想歸理想<br />\n可以學朱凱迪咁話，等到泛民/自決/本土派議席過一半，先可以開展23條立法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但現實還現實 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然大家都冇票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但奶媽或者品客應該係未來5年香港表面上的揸 fit 人<br />\n而且奶媽勝算應該比品客高一幢 IFC<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實問題，奶媽/品客，撐邊個？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  正皮：撐奶媽，永續中聯辦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負皮：撐品客，永續守財奴"},{"pid":"1834e212260010bc591fcb19cae01e8ecd433c13","tid":137612,"uid":3637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:05:00.000Z","msg":"撐胡官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772dd4c5a8ca1b96ed9b2062437997372a94d5b0","tid":137612,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"唔投撐胡官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c53a55e54187de64fc0c0ec00986e4ededbb62","tid":137612,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"撐品客, 然後買定花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd7a45ec66a1c57f2836b9f07430a43bd32383f","tid":137612,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:10:21.000Z","msg":"緊係曾俊華架，守財奴